					<lb xml:id="p2z2"/>Bullingero, amico longe omnium
					<lb xml:id="p2z3"/>colendissimo charissimoque suo
					<lb xml:id="p2z4"/>Bullingero, amico et longo omnino.
					<lb xml:id="p2z5"/>Zürich.
